      "title": "Sri Lanka to increase VAT from September",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe says the Value-Added Tax (VAT) will be increased effective from September 01.",
        "He made this remark presenting the Appropriation (Amendment) Bill, for the remainder of the fiscal year 2022, to the parliament this afternoon.",
        "Accordingly, the VAT will be increased from 12% to 15%, he added."
      ],
